lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a651bbd263ada53d8c87069d543e695a837566f","tid":308774,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撈粗肥牛麻小辣 多汁<br />\n只食<span style=\"color: blue;\">荃灣城市中心</span>後面個間(個間應該係類似原祖店之類，一定正啲)</blockquote><br />\n我都係去呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間好似係舊人自己開唔同老細的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同新舖唔同味<br />\n<br />\n川味以前舊舖就好食，而家開多左新舖就唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年前去開深水埗都會食川味，而家寧願行去長沙灣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a9010a1c66dafa39d9ece39f6c8481f1ee4892","tid":308774,"uid":42432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"識食一定食川味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e4b561d88364fd226dc3c70e4b6ef02a33d564","tid":308774,"uid":174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:03:46.000Z","msg":"以前成日食撈拉面，宜家轉左款面好難食<br />\nBTW, 川味間鋪入面拜齊天大聖<br />\n以前第一次見到覺得勁新奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f832051567b49c6c2ca2c58f0c035af8d4634c56","tid":308774,"uid":121815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好大碗</blockquote><br />\n又平又飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔終於有人識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n次次都嗌撈幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高質過老譚多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平得嚟啲辣度可以自己落<br />\n<br />\n利申 試過一日三餐都去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都試過，好正啊！"},{"pid":"89cd8e487ec5347d7728c7c6a13682c25ec8f1ee","tid":308774,"uid":63339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"下 作為一個瘦嘅女仔 如果食撈薯要加底先飽<br />\n唔覺食薯粉好快肚餓咩"},{"pid":"9cfb2849e69bcf30652c3e6f7ff62d9505cd04aa","tid":308774,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"雲貴香挑你機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a621fa94f9c9adb9420ae3e239185ea7882f6a","tid":308774,"uid":8552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雲貴香挑你機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n湯=雲貴<br />\n撈=川味"},{"pid":"c827098994674ad1ae8d241d08464fd6f37a9c46","tid":308774,"uid":126490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"係抵食囉"},{"pid":"50e7b7a4f41315d3eddd11d1b8124fc5fbe07b47","tid":308774,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"荃灣有三間 邊間先真 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f2a432507b76085eb7de0e28f8fb31f58c9fc8","tid":308774,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3699e93d528540ffdf57df98f123f2f40ba8ab0","tid":308774,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:09:20.000Z","msg":"每個星期最少食兩次撈幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2af4311387f3583250e7ef6c93a812cfe399d1","tid":308774,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荃灣有三間 邊間先真 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話真假 三哥同非三哥既分別"},{"pid":"e4062